item.description:
Manifesting is making what you desire apparent to your eyes and mind. Once "they" know you have clarity... you make a decision and commitment starting in your head. Then actions will follow.

We'll be watching part of a movie and have insightful discussions to help keep you on track. Why not have a brand new start by changing the way you think?

There will be a slight cost ($2-$5) to cover facilitating fees.

Look forward to seeing everyone! 

See you soon :)

Caryn
item.how_to_find_us: Address will be sent when you sign up for meet up
item.name: Let's manifest a new start!
